"reviewcomment":"These guys know what they&#39;re doing! <br><br>In a car-less NYC, it seemed almost impossible to be able to have a nice Christmas tree unless we lugged it home from one of those sidewalk vendors. A quick Google search brought us to the NYC Trees website, where for a very reasonable $109, we got a 6 foot tree, next day delivery, installation, and stand...ALL INCLUSIVE!<br><br>In addition to our tree looking way more beautiful than any of those 2nd rate sidewalk ones, we felt good knowing that our tree was a sustainable one that was sourced from regional farms. The quality is top notch too - the tree looks very healthy, with &#34;full&#34; branches and very minimal needle shedding.<br><br>One of the co-founder brothers himself (Lou) came to deliver and set up our tree and he was super friendly, offering to help move around things to place the tree and trimming the branches so our tree looked perfect. He even watered the tree and gave me tips on how to take care of it - now that&#39;s what I call excellent service!<br><br>If you want your own hassle-free NYC Christmas tree experience, look no further than NYC Trees!",
