"ogimage":"http://s3-media1.ak.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/Dh-h3RWgXUCdmWOce3w-9A/l.jpg",
"rating":"4.5",
"reviewcomment":"Life is good when restaurants carry Everybody Eats! This company is a gluten free persons heaven!!! The bread products are out of this world. Light, fluffy, flavorful unlike most gluten free bread products.   <br>I get so frustrated when we go somewhere that serves GF bread that is crumbly, tasteless, thick and nasty- I tell them about Everybody Eats. My husband and love Astoria&#39;s Sandwich Bar and sometimes he gets a GF one to so we can split our sandwiches. He loves Everybody Eats bread especially the baguette. This place is like no other gf bread. If you haven&#39;t tested it I urge you to run and get some! G-FreeNYC offers it as well as many other locations. I actually haven&#39;t tested the bagels or cookies but have heard all good things. I would love it if Brooklyn Coffee shops in Astoria carried there bagels so we could enjoy the coffee house. This company needs to be in all Astoria restaurants now days!! Wish more natural/health food shops in Astoria had it stocked- maybe someday soon!<br>If your a restaurant owner this is a must have product line- have it stocked! Gf/CD is not going anywhere. The demand for gf product is not to have just anything it&#39;s to have the highest quality gf product as possible. If you have not had Everybody Eats you have to get some today!<br><br>Tips: If you just got diagnosed as CD or need to live a GF lifestyle you will love this company!",
