"reviewcomment":"Similar to Sugar Club grocery store in Elmhurst, Inthira has a wide range of Thai ingredients from Fresh Holy Basil to Frozen Salted Crabs. I&#39;m sure you&#39;ve been looking around for this, and this store is well-stocked with them!<br><br>You can also get all sorts of Canned Thai Curry Pastes, Chili Pastes and Thai Instant Ramen Noodles. Pretty impressive I might say. <br><br>Every time I enter this store, I always make my way to the fridge in the back to grab a bunch or two of Thai Holy Basil. You may wonder what&#39;s a big deal about this. Pad Gaprow (Stir Fried Meat with Spicy Thai Basil Sauce) is supposed to cook with Thai Holy Basil instead of Thai Sweet Basil. It has a distinctive heat and aroma to it. <br><br>The store is easy to get to from 7 train&#39;s 69th Street stop, and they also take credit card with $10 minimum of purchase.",
