"reviewcomment":"My family and I have been loyal customers of calandras for almost 15 years. What can I say about this excellent bakery. I mostly visit the Caldwell location as it&#39;s closer to my house, and the new expansion is beautiful and was much needed! The staff at all 3 locations are always smiling and friendly no matter how many people are in the shop. And I have never seen a more spotless bakery, they obviously pride themselves in cleanliness and I always see the girls cleaning up and straightening out things!!<br>The pastries are literally to die for. The orange crust, ganache covered chocolate mousse, and lobster tails are things I always get going here. Everything is delicious! The bread is freshly baked and the baker is such a sweet heart! Everything is made fresh all day every day, and you get this old time feel from the place. I get my birthday cake every year from here and it&#39;s always just as good as the year before. <br>You won&#39;t be disappointed coming here, I drove nearly 25 miles to come here and it&#39;s worth the trip every time, even if it&#39;s just to stop in and get a cup cake and chat with the girls behind the counter!! Very hard working staff, great product!",
