"ogimage":"http://s3-media2.ak.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/5REs1Gg59GpfI1XiT1ZVYw/l.jpg",
"rating":"4.5",
"reviewcomment":"The person who introduced me to froyo told me to make a pilgrimage to &#34;the froyo store in Bloomingdales&#34; since it was the best. Two years later, I did, and she was SO right! I have tried a lot of froyo and can say I prefer this place for their tart yogurt. If you just want a mound of plain froyo, this is THE place. The portion is bigger than other places and the tart flavor is just the right blend of creamy, tart, and sweet. It was thick and not icy. This is NOT the place to go if you want self-serve, lots of toppings, or a big flavor selection though, so be warned (and there&#39;s definitely a time and place for that).",
