"rating":"4.5",
"reviewcomment":"I always need my dessert fix after breakfast, lunch, and dinner. I decided to yelp a new place to try and came upon this bakery. Though it was a bit of a drive, it was so worth it!!!<br><br>Service: Out of this world, friendly! The guy behind the counter not only greeted us, but offered to explain what everything was since it was our first time at the bakery.<br><br>Pastries: We opted for the Italian cheesecake, pumpkin cheesecake, strawberry shortcake, apple turnover, and cannoli. The apple turnover was warm, chewy/crunchy, and perfectly flavored. The cannoli was crunchy and absolutely delicious. The cream is freshly piped upon ordering and was a bit on the sweet side, but paired with a cappuccino? Perfection! The pumpkin cheesecake was okay; I found the pumpkin flavor too subtle. The Italian cheesecake was AMAZING! Yum! A must try! Their award winning strawberry shortcake delivered as promised! So light and fluffy! Delicious! So good, in fact, that I&#39;m running straight to the fridge after this to finish it!<br><br>Price: Very fair for the quality of the pastries and service! <br><br>Everything here is fresh including their whipped cream! Will definitely have to come back here to try their cookies and other goodies!",
