"reviewcomment":"Based on the reviews with regards to being yelled at by staff, I tried to quietly go in, pick up my items and avoid all eye contact.<br><br>It worked - no one yelled at me! <br><br>On to the food - ABSOLUTELY will make you a believer in raw, whole foods plant-based goodness! <br><br>KELP ME! Summer Noodles - Portion akin to a side dish, this was a cold salad with kelp noodles, julienned carrots and a spicy green sauce. I&#39;m savoring every bite! Acidic and a tad sweet with the right amount of heat! Love kelp noodles - best alternative to carby pasta.<br><br>RAW HUMMUS WRAP - Includes raw falafel, hummus and tahini sauce. Wrapped in leaf lettuce. Really good but got a little wet (perhaps I waited too long to devour it).<br><br>Both cost about $22 so I took a nice fat hit to my wallet but it&#39;s such a nice way to get in fresh vegetables into your diet!",
