"ogimage":"http://s3-media3.ak.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/Ys7r7fLN30zuTKlRpm2MZA/l.jpg",
"rating":"4.0",
"reviewcomment":"Hands down the best bagels in NYC. Tell me where there is a better one and I will personally go there myself. <br><br>Don&#39;t let this little deli feel throw you for a loop. Yes, this place is small, it&#39;s New York so it&#39;s old, not new or shiny and the line is usually to the door. There are only a few small tables inside to eat at, so if you are with another person and a table frees up, my suggestion is to have one person hold the table while the other orders. <br><br>Bagles though get a 5 star! These bagels are hot, fresh and melt in your mouth delicious. How do they get the bread to just melt like that. Bagel lovers know what I&#39;m talking about when you order and your jaw hurts from having to chew?! These are just the opposite. Not sure why I can&#39;t find bagels like these outside of New York...trust me I&#39;ve tried. They do not exist. Please someone prove me wrong though because I&#39;d love a bagel like this in Nashville. <br><br>They have every cream cheese you could want and every type of bagel you want. They of course make lox and sandwiches as well. Go here, only go here. You will not be disappointed. I literally dream of these bagels.",
